      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The air is warmer, the sunsets more orange and the sea more graceful. The roads feel familiar yet it’s the first time I’ve driven many of time. There seem to be more Superspars per square kilometer than cows. Monkey and buck spoor outnumber those of dogs on the beach. ",
            "link": null
          },
