            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I wake in the middle of the night to the sound of a loud ocean. My mind racing. I think about free will and how my friend Matteo believes in it; surely nobody in their right mind would use their free will to wake themself from sleep to think about this right now? Is this not proof in itself of its lack of existence, Matteo? Call me and let’s debate this xx",
